creator: Moe Dress Up Games
descriptionHtml:
💕Do you want to having your own anime princess?💕Do you want to be a fashion designer?💕Come to COCO's world!💕You can creat your own anime princess character!💕Make a wish come ture in COCO's world！
🎀Welcome all girls join in COCO:Anime Princess Dress Up game！It's a free dress up games ,contain offline character Maker, come and design the the most adoreble princess！
🎀Here,you can be a character creator, COCO has colorful contact lens, hair styles, dresses and wonderful costumes.Using them to make COCO a beautiful princess！
🎀You can decorate a sweet room for COCO, make fancy avatars and wallpapers! Use your imagination, creat the most adorable room for COCO!
🎀Clothes are not good enough?Don't like COCO's hair style?It's okay！In COCO:Anime Princess Dress Up Game,you can DIY your own clothes、dresses and hair styles！Come and design a lovely dress for COCO！
🎀Do you want to expirencing the most beautiful fariy tale？Four chapters are waiting for you to unlock them all！Rainbow Island、Snow Kingdom、Wonderland、Moon Castle,every palce has it features,come on！What are you waiting for?
🎀Do you like blindboxes?Then come and get your COCO blindboxes！Variety of blindboxes，each of it has different theme！come and get them all！
🎀Don't forget to share with your friends!
【COCO:Anime Princess Dress Up Game Feature】
👑More than 1000+ dress up items and costume!
👑All free: 100% free of all content!
👑Mode selection: You can choose single mode or double-person mode whatever you want！
👑style switch:switch different style you like:gothic、elegant、cute、cool......
👑adoreble makeup,beautiful nails,you can make COCO a cutest princess！
👑Various kinds of costume for COCO,such as,western festival suits,LOLITA,traditional Chinese festivals suits,traditional Japenese suits,fashion suits,fairy theme suits and more,are waiting for you to unlock them all！
【In COCO:Anime Princess Dress Up game you can】
🎀Make COCO a beautiful anime princess!
🎀Have your own anime princess!
🎀Collect all lovely features you love!
🎀Experience the life simulation of a fashion princess!
🌈Come and enjoy the princess journey! 🌈

💖【Contact Us】💖
💖—Email：melestudio@hotmail.com
